{"tid":2345733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好跟車太貼 習近平手術消息難以核實","createTime":"2020-12-29T18:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T18:40:41.000Z","uid":74303,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2988e829fe0155a8a1c15e9002d07ac4805d8527","tid":2345733,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T18:10:54.000Z","msg":"【希望之聲2020年12月29日】（本台記者岳文驍綜合報導）從12月27日開始，推特盛傳中共總書記習近平將因顱內動脈瘤接受手術治療。由於事態關鍵，已成立 特別危機辦。但相關消息目前難以核實。<br />\n<br />\n據推特多方消息，初步的信息源來自於一個阿根廷人的賬號，據稱，此人與香港的一位腦瘤專家交情極深，屬於&ldquo;鐵哥們&rdquo;的關係。<br />\n<br />\n汁： <a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/458374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F458374&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=273e8efb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/458374</a>"},{"pid":"384ec7baef92d34b8f8e6a156d88d7a085f04d94","tid":2345733,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T18:22:44.000Z","msg":"D 買account 又出post䕶航，單嘢真係唔簡單"},{"pid":"4d904b3def824060ce3bf2680b60fab3afc8df5a","tid":2345733,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T18:40:41.000Z","msg":"假啦，封鎖消息咁快點會比人知到"}]}